        {
            "title": "資產管理公司:摩根士丹利認為第一季財報預期存在下行風險",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/LJqIY01RxhNX5qG6JbAjFg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPED410M6_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"摩根士丹利\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:摩根士丹利;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/摩根士丹利\">摩根士丹利</a>在4月中旬第一季財報季來臨前,對傳統<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"資產管理公司\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:資產管理公司;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/資產管理公司\">資產管理公司</a>持謹慎態度,下調該類股整體預期,並警告近期的優異表現可能使估值面臨風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師Michael Cyprys將第一季每股盈餘預期平均下調0.7%,使其預測比市場共識高出約1.2%,並將2026年和2027年全年每股盈餘預期各下調3%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">雖然這些數字目前與市場共識大致一致,但摩根士丹利指出其營業收入預測比市場預期低1%至2%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-48f43fc9-8624-3498-aadc-7d785ba46627-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">第一季下調幅度最大的是貝萊德(BlackRock),Cyprys將其每股盈餘預期下調11.9%,理由是預期績效費用較低。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">摩根士丹利將貝萊德的目標價從1,550美元下調至1,368美元,但仍維持增持評級。WisdomTree Investments的上調幅度最大,達4.2%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Virtus Investment Partners的目標價下調幅度最大,下降19%至125美元,反映出摩根士丹利認為第一季隱含資金外流的年化衰減率約為26%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管語氣謹慎,摩根士丹利指出,截至目前為止,業界互惠基金和ETF資金流入達3,090億美元,是去年同期的兩倍多,主要由ETF推動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Cyprys寫道:「對傳統資產管理公司持謹慎態度,因其今年迄今相較於其他研究標的已大幅跑贏14個百分點,市場對傳統資產管理公司定價相對反映了更多利好消息。但我們認為存在風險。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B3%87%E7%94%A2%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8-%E6%91%A9%E6%A0%B9%E5%A3%AB%E4%B8%B9%E5%88%A9%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E7%AC%AC-%E5%AD%A3%E8%B2%A1%E5%A0%B1%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F%E5%AD%98%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%8B%E8%A1%8C%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA-175313021.html",
